TY  - JOUR
TI  - On Equilibrium in Graham's Model of World Trade and Other Competitive Systems
AU  - McKenzie, Lionel
AB  - [The existence and uniqueness of competitive equilibrium in Graham's model of international trade is proved by using Kakutani's fixed point theorem. The method of this proof is sufficiently general that it may be applied to other competitive models in which Graham's restrictive assumptions have been considerably relaxed.]
C1  - Full publication date: Apr., 1954
DB  - JSTOR
